  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Supporting international efforts to build Somalia's long term security and stability
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Explanation of Vote by Sonia Farrey, UK Political Coordinator at the UN, on the Security Council resolution on Somalia</p>

  </div>
</div>

