  <img class="app-c-figure__image" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/80653/Screen_Shot_2020-11-12_at_12.01.04_PM.png" alt="Sonia Farrey, UK Political Coordinator at the UN"></img>
